source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_1<tab>Greetings! I take it you have come to see me about a retainer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_1<tab>Приветствую! Я так понимаю, вы пришли ко мне по поводу слуг.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_2<tab>Retainers are hardworking lads and lasses who will help you to manage those spoils earned while off slaying dragons or whatever it is you adventurers do.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_2<tab>Слуги — это трудолюбивые парни и девушки, которые помогут вам распорядиться добычей, заработанной во время истребления драконов или того, чем вы, искатели приключений обычно занимаетесь.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_3<tab>Unfortunately, you do not appear you could even slay an eft, let alone a dragon, therefore I must decline any petition you may have to take a retainer into your employ.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_3<tab>К сожалению, вы, похоже, не способны сразить даже эфта, не говоря уже о драконе, поэтому я вынужден отклонить любое ваше прошение о найме слуги на вашу службу.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_4<tab>Build yourself a reputation in this city, however, and I shall provide you with whatever it is you need. Might I suggest you start by heading back to the Adventurers' Guild and seeing if someone there has work for you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_4<tab>Заработайте себе репутацию в этом городе, и я обеспечу вас всем необходимым. Могу я предложить вам для начала вернуться в Гильдию искателей приключений и узнать, нет ли у кого-нибудь там работы для вас?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_TITLE<tab>What would you like to do?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_TITLE<tab>Что вы хотели бы сделать?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_TALK<tab>Small Talk.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_TALK<tab>Поговорить.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_CREATE<tab>Hire a retainer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_CREATE<tab>Нанять слугу.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REMOVE<tab>Release a retainer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REMOVE<tab>Отпустить слугу.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REMAKE<tab>Change a retainer's appearance and nickname.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REMAKE<tab>Изменить имя или внешность слуги.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_EXPLANATION<tab>Ask about retainers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_EXPLANATION<tab>Спросить про слуг.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_JOBCHANGE<tab>Inquire about retainer jobs.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_JOBCHANGE<tab>Узнать о профессиях слуг.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_CHECK_CASHBACK<tab>View market tax rates.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_CHECK_CASHBACK<tab>Посмотреть налоги на рынках.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Nothing.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Ничего.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_LIMSA<tab>Отправить слугу в Лимса Ломинсу.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_GRIDANIA<tab>Dispatch a retainer to Gridania.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_GRIDANIA<tab>Отправить слугу в Гриданию.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_ULDAH<tab>Dispatch a retainer to Ul'dah.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_ULDAH<tab>Отправить слугу в Уль'ду.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_ISHGARD<tab>Dispatch a retainer to Ishgard.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_ISHGARD<tab>Отправить слугу в Ишгард.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_TOWN40<tab>Отправить слугу в Куганэ.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_OLDSHARLAYAN<tab>Dispatch a retainer to Old Sharlayan.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER_OLDSHARLAYAN<tab>Отправить слугу в Старый Шарлеан.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_TITLE<tab>What will you ask?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_TITLE<tab>Что вы спросите?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_WHAT_IS<tab>Who are retainers?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_WHAT_IS<tab>Кто такие слуги?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_ABOUT<tab>What services can retainers provide?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_ABOUT<tab>Что могут делать слуги?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_CALL<tab>How do I summon a retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_CALL<tab>Как призвать слугу?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_BACK<tab>Nothing
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_BACK<tab>Ничего

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ABOUT_TALK_01<tab>Retainers are men and women who offer their services in exchange for coin. Though they're seldom as sharp as adventurers like yourself, they're no strangers to life's more menial tasks─tasks which your lot might not think worth your time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ABOUT_TALK_01<tab>Retainers are men and women who offer their services in exchange for coin. Though they're seldom as sharp as adventurers like yourself, they're no strangers to life's more menial tasks─tasks which your lot might not think worth your time.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ABOUT_TALK_02<tab>Retainers can provide a host of different services, from tending your items to protecting your gil. Oh, and you need not worry about providing recompense for a retainer's services, for the Adventurers' Guild will not only cover his salary, but also replace anything that goes missing, should you wake up to find your belongings gone and your retainer nowhere to be found.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ABOUT_TALK_02<tab>Retainers can provide a host of different services, from tending your items to protecting your gil. Oh, and you need not worry about providing recompense for a retainer's services, for the Adventurers' Guild will not only cover his salary, but also replace anything that goes missing, should you wake up to find your belongings gone and your retainer nowhere to be found.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ITEMS_GIL_TALK_01<tab>Another job retainers are often asked to perform is the tending of items placed up for sale in the markets─something many adventurers cannot be bothered to do themselves.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ITEMS_GIL_TALK_01<tab>Another job retainers are often asked to perform is the tending of items placed up for sale in the markets─something many adventurers cannot be bothered to do themselves.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ITEMS_GIL_TALK_02<tab>If you wish to experience the market for yourself, I ask that you seek out one of the nearby boards.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ITEMS_GIL_TALK_02<tab>If you wish to experience the market for yourself, I ask that you seek out one of the nearby boards.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CALL_TALK_01<tab>Retainers in your employ can be summoned at any time using special bells like the one nearby.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CALL_TALK_01<tab>Ваших слуг можно вызвать в любое время с помощью специальных колокольчиков, таких как тот, что находится рядом.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CALL_TALK_02<tab>Summoning bells can also be found around the realm in oft-visited locations such as city markets and inns.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CALL_TALK_02<tab>Summoning bells can also be found around the realm in oft-visited locations such as city markets and inns.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_ASK_ABOUT<tab>Learn about Market Tax
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_ASK_ABOUT<tab>Узнать больше о рыночных налогах

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_EXPLANATION<tab>To make their markets more attractive to prospective sellers, cities will often lower the percentage of tax that is collected from each sale.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_EXPLANATION<tab>To make their markets more attractive to prospective sellers, cities will often lower the percentage of tax that is collected from each sale.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_CAUTION<tab>Reduced tax rate periods can end earlier than indicated if areas require maintenance.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_CAUTION<tab>Reduced tax rate periods can end earlier than indicated if areas require maintenance.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_TALK_01<tab>According to our records, you may hire up to <var 20 E802 /var> retainers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_TALK_01<tab>Согласно нашим данным, вы можете нанять слуг в количестве <var 20 E802 /var>, и не более.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NO_RETAINERS_TALK<tab>Currently, you have no retainers in your employ.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NO_RETAINERS_TALK<tab>В настоящее время у вас в штате нет ни одного слуги.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_HAVE_RETAINERS_TALK<tab>Currently, you have <var 20 E802 /var> <var 08 E4E80202 ((retainer)) ((retainers)) /var> in your employ.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_HAVE_RETAINERS_TALK<tab>В настоящее время у вас на работе <var 20 E802 /var> <var 08 E4E80202 ((слуга)) ((слуг)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CUSTOMIZE_WARNING<tab>While customizing your retainer, you will be unable to communicate with players and engage in other activities.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CUSTOMIZE_WARNING<tab>Во время оформления слуги для вас, вы не сможете общаться с другими игроками и заниматься различными видами деятельности.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CUSTOMIZE_TALK<tab>Excellent. We have quite a few men and women on our lists, so I invite you to describe the retainer you desire, down to the most minute detail.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CUSTOMIZE_TALK<tab>Превосходно. В наших списках довольно много мужчин и женщин, поэтому я предлагаю вам описать какого слугу вы желаете, вплоть до мельчайших деталей.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_WARNING<tab>Beginning the retainer customization process will automatically cancel your Duty Finder registration.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_WARNING<tab>Beginning the retainer customization process will automatically cancel your Duty Finder registration.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_CONFIRM<tab>Withdraw duty registration and hire a retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_CONFIRM<tab>Отменить регистрацию на миссию и нанять слугу?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TALK<tab>I can think of several retainers that are exactly as you describe. Oddly enough, they have strikingly different personalities. If you would be so kind as to state a preference, it would be most helpful.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TALK<tab>Я могу вспомнить несколько слуг, которые выглядят точно так же, как вы описали. Как ни странно, у них поразительно разные характеры. Если вы будете так любезны, укажете свои предпочтения, это было бы очень полезно.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TITLE<tab>Select your retainer's personality.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TITLE<tab>Выберите характер вашего слуги.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_CHEERFUL<tab>Polite.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_CHEERFUL<tab>Вежливый.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_WILD<tab>Rough.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_WILD<tab>Грубый.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_COOLHEADED<tab>Serious.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_COOLHEADED<tab>Серьёзный.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_CAREFREE<tab>Carefree.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_CAREFREE<tab>Беззаботный.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_PROBLEMATIC<tab>Independent.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_PROBLEMATIC<tab>Независимый.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_PLAYFUL<tab>Lively.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_PLAYFUL<tab>Оживлённый.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_ENTER<tab>Very well, I have just the individual in mind. When summoned, this retainer will greet you just so:
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_ENTER<tab>Очень хорошо, у меня как раз есть такой человек на примете. Когда вы его позовёте, этот слуга поприветствует вас именно так:

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_LEAVE<tab>And when dismissed, this retainer will bid you farewell just so:
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_LEAVE<tab>И при отзыве этот слуга попрощается с вами именно так:

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_CONFIRM<tab>Hire this retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_CONFIRM<tab>Нанять этого слугу?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_ASK<tab>Excellent. It is also customary to give a retainer an appellation of one's own making─a nickname, as it were. We find this deepens the bond between our clients and their retainers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_ASK<tab>Превосходно. Кроме того, принято называть своего клиента по имени — так сказать, по прозвищу что вы ему дадите. Мы считаем, что это углубляет связь между нашими клиентами и их помощниками.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_TITLE<tab>Retainer Nickname
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_TITLE<tab>Псевдоним слуги

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_MESSAGE0<tab>Give your retainer a nickname.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_MESSAGE0<tab>Дайте вашему слуге псевдоним.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_MESSAGE1<tab>Names must be at least 3 characters long and can contain letters, apostrophes, and hyphens. Please note, however, that hyphens cannot be used in succession or placed immediately before or after apostrophes.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_MESSAGE1<tab>Имя должно состоять из хотя бы 3 символов и может содержать буквы, апострофы и дефисы. Пожалуйста, учтите, что нельзя поставить несколько дефисов подряд или поставить их сразу перед или после апострофов.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_HEAD<tab>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_HEAD<tab>

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CANCEL_CONFIRM<tab>Are you certain you wish to cancel the hiring process?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CANCEL_CONFIRM<tab>Вы точно хотите остановить процесс найма?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_CONFIRM<tab>Hire the services of <var 29 EA02 /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_CONFIRM<tab>Нанять слугу <var 29 EA02 /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE<tab>Hire a retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE<tab>Нанять слугу?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE_YES<tab>Yes
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE_YES<tab>Да

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE_NO<tab>No
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE_NO<tab>Нет

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATING_RETAINER<tab>One moment, please, while I draft the proper documentation.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATING_RETAINER<tab>Одну минуту, пожалуйста, пока я подготовлю соответствующую документацию.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_01<tab>Congratulations! <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> is now in your employ.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_01<tab>Поздравляю! <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> теперь в вашем распоряжении.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_02<tab>You can summon your new retainer using the nearby bell.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_02<tab>Вы можете вызвать своего нового слугу с помощью колокольчика, расположенного неподалеку.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_03<tab>If you have any further questions or requests, please do not hesitate to ask.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_03<tab>Если у вас есть дополнительные вопросы или пожелания, пожалуйста, не стесняйтесь спрашивать.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FAILED_NAME<tab>The name you have chosen is not available. Please select another.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FAILED_NAME<tab>Выбранное вами имя недоступно. Пожалуйста, введите другое.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FULL<tab>I am sorry, but you cannot hire any more retainers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FULL<tab>I am sorry, but you cannot hire any more retainers.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_CANCEL<tab>Understood. If you change your mind, speak with me again.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_CANCEL<tab>Понятно. Если вы передумаете, поговорите со мной ещё раз.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_TALK_LIMSA_01<tab>Select the retainer you wish to send to the markets in Limsa Lominsa.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_TALK_LIMSA_01<tab>Выберите слугу, которого вы хотите отправить на рынки Лимса Ломинсы.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_LIMSA<tab>Send <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> to Limsa Lominsa?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_LIMSA<tab>Отправить <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> в Лимса Ломинсу?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_SUCCESS_LIMSA<tab><var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> был отправлен в Лимса Ломинсу.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ALREADY_LIMSA<tab>Этот слуга уже в Лимса Ломинсе.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ALREADY_ULDAH<tab>Этот слуга уже в Уль'де.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_TALK_TOWN40_01<tab>Выберите слугу, которого вы хотите отправить на рынки Куганэ.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_TALK_OLDSHARLAYAN_01<tab>Select the retainer you wish to send to the markets in Old Sharlayan.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_TALK_OLDSHARLAYAN_01<tab>Выберите слугу, которого вы хотите отправить на рынки Старого Шарлеана.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ALREADY_OLDSHARLAYAN<tab>Этот слуга уже в Старом Шарлеане.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_YES<tab>Yes
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_YES<tab>Да

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_NO<tab>No
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_NO<tab>Нет

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_RETAINER_EXPLANATION<tab>You...are dissatisfied with one of your retainers? Very well. If you would be so kind as to inform me which retainer is lacking, we can begin the review process.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_RETAINER_EXPLANATION<tab>Вы... недовольны одним из ваших слуг? Очень хорошо. Если вы будете так любезны, сообщите мне, в каком из них есть недостаток, мы сможем начать процесс рассмотрения проблемы.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_RETAINER_TALK<tab>You may change your retainers' nicknames or instruct them to visit the aesthetician at any time. If you desire more drastic changes to a retainer's appearance or personality, the retainer vocate will assist you in finding a replacement of comparable skill and experience.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_RETAINER_TALK<tab>You may change your retainers' nicknames or instruct them to visit the aesthetician at any time. If you desire more drastic changes to a retainer's appearance or personality, the retainer vocate will assist you in finding a replacement of comparable skill and experience.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE<tab>Review your specifications for <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE<tab>Review your specifications for <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE_YES<tab>Yes
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE_YES<tab>Да

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE_NO<tab>No
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE_NO<tab>Нет

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_CANCEL<tab>Then you <var 1A 02 /var>are<var 1A 01 /var> completely satisfied with your retainer? Understood. Pray speak with me again should your preferences change.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_CANCEL<tab><var 1A 02 /var>, вы полностью удовлетворены своим слугой? Понятно. Пожалуйста, свяжитесь со мной снова, если ваши предпочтения изменятся.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Withdraw duty registration and review your retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Withdraw duty registration and review your retainer?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_TALK<tab>Very well. First, let us review your retainer's current appearance. I must ask that you describe in detail which aspects you find unappealing, and what you would prefer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_TALK<tab>Очень хорошо. Во-первых, давайте рассмотрим текущий внешний вид вашего слуги. Я должен попросить вас подробно описать, какие аспекты вы считаете непривлекательными, и что бы вы предпочли изменить.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TALK_REMAKE<tab>I see... Next, I would have you confirm your preference with regards to personality. “The right retainer for the right person,” as we are wont to say.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TALK_REMAKE<tab>I see... Next, I would have you confirm your preference with regards to personality. “The right retainer for the right person,” as we are wont to say.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_REMAKE_ENTER<tab>To ensure there is no misunderstanding, know that your retainer will address you just so:
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_REMAKE_ENTER<tab>To ensure there is no misunderstanding, know that your retainer will address you just so:

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Are you satisfied with this personality?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Are you satisfied with this personality?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_ASK_REMAKE<tab>Understood. Finally, I must needs verify the nickname you would give your retainer. You may register the same nickname if you like.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_ASK_REMAKE<tab>Понятно. Наконец, я должен уточнить, какое имя вы хотите дать своему слуге. Вы можете зарегистрировать то же имя что и у вас, если хотите.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CANCEL_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Are you certain you wish to cancel the review process?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CANCEL_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Are you certain you wish to cancel the review process?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_CONFIRM<tab>Complete your review of <var 29 EA02 /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_CONFIRM<tab>Complete your review of <var 29 EA02 /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMEKE_RETAINER<tab>One moment, please, while I draft the proper documentation.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMEKE_RETAINER<tab>Одну минуту, пожалуйста, пока я подготовлю соответствующую документацию.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EQUIP_HAVE_RETAINER<tab>Forgive me, but you must first instruct your retainer to remove all equipment. A necessary precaution, in light of past incidents.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EQUIP_HAVE_RETAINER<tab>Forgive me, but you must first instruct your retainer to remove all equipment. A necessary precaution, in light of past incidents.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_VENTURE_RETAINER<tab>Our records indicate that your retainer is currently undertaking a venture. Until that is no longer the case, I fear we cannot begin the review process.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_VENTURE_RETAINER<tab>Our records indicate that your retainer is currently undertaking a venture. Until that is no longer the case, I fear we cannot begin the review process.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_FAILED<tab>Due to unforeseen circumstances, we cannot review your retainer at this time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_FAILED<tab>Due to unforeseen circumstances, we cannot review your retainer at this time.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_SUCCESS_01<tab>I am pleased to inform you that your review has been processed, and <var 29 EA02 /var> is now ready to serve you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_SUCCESS_01<tab>I am pleased to inform you that your review has been processed, and <var 29 EA02 /var> is now ready to serve you.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_SUCCESS_02<tab>You can summon your retainer using the nearby bell.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_SUCCESS_02<tab>Вы можете вызвать своего слугу с помощью колокольчика, расположенного неподалеку.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_RETAINER_EXPLANATION<tab>Very well. Allow me a moment to locate your documentation.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_RETAINER_EXPLANATION<tab>Очень хорошо. Дайте мне минутку, чтобы найти вашу документацию.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NO_RETAINERS_AVAILABLE<tab>It does not appear you have any retainers in your employ at this time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NO_RETAINERS_AVAILABLE<tab>It does not appear you have any retainers in your employ at this time.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_RETAINER_TALK<tab>Confirm the retainer you wish to release.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_RETAINER_TALK<tab>Выберите слугу, которого вы хотели бы отпустить.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE<tab>Release <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE<tab>Отпустить <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var>?

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_HASHOUSE<tab>Release <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var>?
Please be advised that retainers placed in estates will not be automatically removed.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_HASHOUSE<tab>Отпустить <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var>?
Имейте в виду, что слуги, поставленные в жилой площади, не будут автоматически убраны.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_YES<tab>Yes
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_YES<tab>Да

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_NO<tab>No
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_NO<tab>Нет

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_SUCCESS<tab><var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> is released from service.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_SUCCESS<tab>Вы отпустили <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_FAILED_INVENTORY<tab>Our records show that the retainer you wish to release is still in possession of several of your belongings, and may have placed a number of them for sale on the market. You must retrieve those belongings before I can approve the dismissal.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_FAILED_INVENTORY<tab>Our records show that the retainer you wish to release is still in possession of several of your belongings, and may have placed a number of them for sale on the market. You must retrieve those belongings before I can approve the dismissal.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_CANCEL<tab>Understood. The retainer shall remain in your employ. Speak with me again if you change your mind.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_CANCEL<tab>Понятно. Слуга останется в вашем распоряжении. Обращайтесь ко мне снова, если что-то захотите изменить.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_TITLE<tab>What would you like to do?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_TITLE<tab>Что вы хотели бы сделать?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_HOWTO<tab>Ask about assigning your retainer a job.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_HOWTO<tab>Спросить о назначении профессии слуге.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_RELATION<tab>Ask about job requirements.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_OBTAIN<tab>Purchase a copy of <var 1A 02 /var>Modern Vocation<var 1A 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Nothing.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Ничего.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_01<tab>By popular demand, we have prepared an exhaustive publication to aid clients who would have their retainers train in certain ancient or esoteric traditions.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_01<tab>By popular demand, we have prepared an exhaustive publication to aid clients who would have their retainers train in certain ancient or esoteric traditions.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_02<tab>To assign your retainer a <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>job<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, you must first obtain <var 31 ((Item)) 02E8020202 /var>, which can be purchased from the retainer vocate for 40 ventures.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_02<tab>To assign your retainer a <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>job<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, you must first obtain <var 31 ((Item)) 02E8020202 /var>, which can be purchased from the retainer vocate for 40 ventures.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_03<tab>Furthermore, you must have achieved level 50 in the job you wish to assign your retainer. Please note that the jobs you can assign your retainer are determined by their class. Limited jobs are not available.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_03<tab>Furthermore, you must have achieved level 50 in the job you wish to assign your retainer. Please note that the jobs you can assign your retainer are determined by their class. Limited jobs are not available.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_04<tab>If you wish to assign a level 50 retainer a job which is not currently available, you will need to reset and change their class.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_04<tab>If you wish to assign a level 50 retainer a job which is not currently available, you will need to reset and change their class.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_TALK_01<tab>As you may know, a certain measure of experience is required before a retainer may train in a more advanced tradition.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_TALK_01<tab>As you may know, a certain measure of experience is required before a retainer may train in a more advanced tradition.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Hyuran Female-)With your leave, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Hyuran Female-)Don't you worry 'bout a thing. I got this.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Hyuran Female-)Don't you worry 'bout a thing. I got this.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Hyuran Female-)Farewell, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Hyuran Female-)Farewell, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Hyuran Female-)If there is nothing else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, I'll be going now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Hyuran Female-)If there is nothing else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, I'll be going now.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Hyuran Female-)Is that all? Very well, until next time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Независимая хьюр-женщина-) Это всё? Очень хорошо, до следующего раза.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Hyuran Female-)Oh, will that be all today? Very well, but promise me you'll come back soon!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Жизнерадостная хьюр-женщина) О, это всё на сегодня? Очень хорошо, но обещай, что вернётесь как можно скорее!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Elezen Male-)As always, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, it has been an honor and a privilege.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Elezen Male-)As always, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, it has been an honor and a privilege.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Elezen Male-)You can count on me, chief─I know how to get things done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Elezen Male-)You can count on me, chief─I know how to get things done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Elezen Male-)Don't be a stranger.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Elezen Male-)Don't be a stranger.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Elezen Male-)I swear it shall be done. Eventually.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Elezen Male-)I swear it shall be done. Eventually.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Elezen Male-)As you wish.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Elezen Male-)As you wish.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Elezen Male-)Capital! I shall carry out your orders forthwith.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Elezen Male-)Capital! I shall carry out your orders forthwith.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Elezen Female-)I humbly await your next summons, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Elezen Female-)I humbly await your next summons, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Elezen Female-)Don't leave me alone for too long, hear?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Elezen Female-)Don't leave me alone for too long, hear?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Elezen Female-)Always a pleasure.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Elezen Female-)Always a pleasure.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Elezen Female-)That will be all, yes? Then if you would excuse me...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Elezen Female-)That will be all, yes? Then if you would excuse me...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Elezen Female-)I believe that concludes our dealings for now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Elezen Female-)I believe that concludes our dealings for now.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Elezen Female-)Are you certain you don't desire anything else? Anything at all? Very well, I shall take my leave.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Дизнерадостная элезен-женщина-)Вы уверены, что не желаете ничего другого? Вообще ничего? Хорошо, я ухожу.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Lalafellin Male-)Your every whim shall be swiftly carried out with due care and consideration.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Lalafellin Male-)Your every whim shall be swiftly carried out with due care and consideration.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Lalafellin Male-)Shouldn't take more than a moment, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Lalafellin Male-)Shouldn't take more than a moment, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Lalafellin Male-)I'll be going, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Серьёзный Лалафель-мужчина-)Тогда я пойду.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Lalafellin Male-)Thank the gods we're finished. I've got plans to put my hands in places I've never seen...if you know what I mean.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Lalafellin Male-)Thank the gods we're finished. I've got plans to put my hands in places I've never seen...if you know what I mean.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Lalafellin Male-)Be well.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Lalafellin Male-)Be well.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Lalafellin Male-)I'm off, I'm off!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Lalafellin Male-)I'm off, I'm off!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Lalafellin Female-)Until we meet again!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Lalafellin Female-)Until we meet again!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Lalafellin Female-)Blessin's o' the Twelve upon ye.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Lalafellin Female-)Blessin's o' the Twelve upon ye.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Lalafellin Female-)May Nald'thal see fit to fatten our pockets!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Lalafellin Female-)May Nald'thal see fit to fatten our pockets!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Lalafellin Female-)Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Your wish is my command, and so forth.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Lalafellin Female-)Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Your wish is my command, and so forth.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Lalafellin Female-)You know how to reach me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Lalafellin Female-)You know how to reach me.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Lalafellin Female-)Is it time for good-byes already? I'm going to miss you...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Lalafellin Female-)Is it time for good-byes already? I'm going to miss you...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Miqo'te Male-)Thy will be done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Miqo'te Male-)Thy will be done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Miqo'te Male-)The markets may be a bleedin' battlefield, but I'm a godsdamned soldier. You can count on me, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Miqo'te Male-)The markets may be a bleedin' battlefield, but I'm a godsdamned soldier. You can count on me, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Miqo'te Male-)...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Miqo'te Male-)...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Miqo'te Male-)Why so serrrious? <sigh> So it goes.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Miqo'te Male-)Why so serrrious? <sigh> So it goes.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Miqo'te Male-)I hardly think that warranted my personal appearance, but what is done is done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Miqo'te Male-)I hardly think that warranted my personal appearance, but what is done is done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Miqo'te Male-)Then I have satisfied your every need? Excellent! I do so take pleasure in servicing my clients.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Жизнерадостный мико'те-мужчина-) Значит, я удовлетворил все ваши потребности? Превосходно! Я получаю огромное удовольствие, обслуживая своих клиентов.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Miqo'te Female-)Good-bye for now, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Miqo'te Female-)Good-bye for now, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Miqo'te Female-)Right then, let's get on with it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Miqo'te Female-)Right then, let's get on with it!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Miqo'te Female-)There is no call for concerrrn.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Miqo'te Female-)There is no call for concerrrn.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Miqo'te Female-)When the master's away, the cat will play.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Miqo'te Female-)When the master's away, the cat will play.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Miqo'te Female-)Gods, this is tirin'...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Miqo'te Female-)Gods, this is tirin'...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Miqo'te Female-)You don't want to be with me anymore? <sniffle>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Miqo'te Female-)You don't want to be with me anymore? <sniffle>

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Roegadyn Male-)I shall carry out your wishes as instructed, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Roegadyn Male-)I shall carry out your wishes as instructed, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Roegadyn Male-)Bwahahaha! I'm in yer bazaar, sellin' yer wares!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Roegadyn Male-)Bwahahaha! I'm in yer bazaar, sellin' yer wares!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Roegadyn Male-)I will go now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Roegadyn Male-)I will go now.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Roegadyn Male-)Awww, bugger. Reckon I best get to work...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Roegadyn Male-)Awww, bugger. Reckon I best get to work...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Roegadyn Male-)I don't do good-byes.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Roegadyn Male-)I don't do good-byes.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Roegadyn Male-)Go and grab yourself some shut-eye, chief. You look terrible!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Roegadyn Male-)Go and grab yourself some shut-eye, chief. You look terrible!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Roegadyn Female-)Will that be all for today, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>? Understood.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Вежливая Рогадин-женщина-)Это всё на сегодня, <var 08 E905 ((миледи)) ((милорд)) /var>? Поняла.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Roegadyn Female-)Aye, aye, cap'n!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Roegadyn Female-)Aye, aye, cap'n!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Roegadyn Female-)Duly noted.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Roegadyn Female-)Duly noted.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Roegadyn Female-)Not exactly how I was hopin' to spend my day, but I suppose it can't be helped.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Roegadyn Female-)Not exactly how I was hopin' to spend my day, but I suppose it can't be helped.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Roegadyn Female-)Ours is not to reason why. Ours is but to do and die.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Roegadyn Female-)Ours is not to reason why. Ours is but to do and die.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Roegadyn Female-)Ever the consummate professional, I see. Another time, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Roegadyn Female-)Ever the consummate professional, I see. Another time, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Auri Male-)If there is nothing else, then I shall take my leave.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Auri Male-)If there is nothing else, then I shall take my leave.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Auri Male-)Is that all? Guess I'll be on my way, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Auri Male-)Is that all? Guess I'll be on my way, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Auri Male-)Any last requests? Very well. Heh heh heh... Ahem.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Серьёзный ауранец-)Ещё что-нибудь? Очень хорошо. Хе-хе-хе... Кхм.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Auri Male-)Ah, yes, of course. Duty calls!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Auri Male-)Ah, yes, of course. Duty calls!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Auri Male-)You are finished with me, then?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Auri Male-)You are finished with me, then?

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Auri Male-)Here today and gone tomorrow;♪
Yes, I know─♪
That is so!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Auri Male-)Here today and gone tomorrow;♪
Yes, I know─♪
That is so!♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Auri Female-)If ever you have need of me, just ring.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Вежливая ауранка-)Если я вам понадоблюсь, просто позовите.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Auri Female-)Always a pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Auri Female-)Always a pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Auri Female-)Right, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Auri Female-)Right, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Auri Female-)Finished already? Guess that's that, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Auri Female-)Finished already? Guess that's that, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Auri Female-)You're leaving already? Fine, then! I-It's not like I wanted you to stay or anything.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Auri Female-)You're leaving already? Fine, then! I-It's not like I wanted you to stay or anything.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Auri Female-)Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Very good indeed!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Auri Female-)Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Very good indeed!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Hrothgar Male-)Always a pleasure to serve, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Hrothgar Male-)Always a pleasure to serve, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Hrothgar Male-)Hmph. I hope that next time you will have a more meaningful task for me.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Hrothgar Male-)<var 1A 02 /var>Good-bye<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Hrothgar Male-)<var 1A 02 /var>Good-bye<var 1A 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Hrothgar Male-)And with that, I shall be off. Places to go, people to see.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Hrothgar Male-)And with that, I shall be off. Places to go, people to see.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Indepedent Hrothgar Male-)Bahahaha! Till next time, my friend!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Indepedent Hrothgar Male-)Bahahaha! Till next time, my friend!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Hrothgar Male-)Ring for me whenever you please! You know that I will never let you down!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Hrothgar Male-)Ring for me whenever you please! You know that I will never let you down!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Viera Female-)Must we part so soon?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Viera Female-)Must we part so soon?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Viera Female-)And I am off!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Viera Female-)And I am off!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Viera Female-)Call on me as you please. If I am so inclined, I will answer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Viera Female-)Call on me as you please. If I am so inclined, I will answer.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Viera Female-)That is all, I suppose...? <yawn> Very well...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Беззаботная виера-женщина) Это всё, я полагаю...? <зевок> Очень хорошо...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Indepedent Viera Female-)That is all? Oh, I was hoping there'd be more...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Indepedent Viera Female-)That is all? Oh, I was hoping there'd be more...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Viera Female-)Is that all you need of me? But I could yet serve you in so many ways!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Viera Female-)Is that all you need of me? But I could yet serve you in so many ways!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Viera Male-)Do not hesitate to call upon me again. Fare you well in your endeavors, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>(-Polite Viera Male-)Do not hesitate to call upon me again. Fare you well in your endeavors, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Viera Male-)Just say the word, yer <var 08 E905 ((ladyship)) ((lordship)) /var>, and I'll be here with bells on.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>(-Rough Viera Male-)Just say the word, yer <var 08 E905 ((ladyship)) ((lordship)) /var>, and I'll be here with bells on.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Serious Viera Male-)If you have no further need of my services...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>(-Серьёзный Виера мужчина-)Если вам больше не нужны мои услуги...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Viera Male-)I'm off for another glass, then. You know where to find me!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>(-Carefree Viera Male-)I'm off for another glass, then. You know where to find me!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Viera Male-)What─is that it? Are you <var 1A 02 /var>sure<var 1A 01 /var> you need a retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>(-Independent Viera Male-)What─is that it? Are you <var 1A 02 /var>sure<var 1A 01 /var> you need a retainer?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Viera Male-)Nothing else? Then I shall be hopping along.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>(-Lively Viera Male-)Nothing else? Then I shall be hopping along.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_ORDER_FAILED_NO_CHARGE<tab>You cannot perform this action until you have purchased the services of an additional retainer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_ORDER_FAILED_NO_CHARGE<tab>Вы не можете сделать это. Вам нужно сначала приобрести сервисы дополнительного слуги.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_INVENTORY_EXPLANATION<tab>You cannot release retainers while they are in possession of any items or gil.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_INVENTORY_EXPLANATION<tab>Вы не можете отпустить слугу, когда у него есть предметы или гилы.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_EXPLANATION_01<tab>What would you like to know?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_EXPLANATION_01<tab>Что вы хотели бы узнать?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_FAILED<tab>You were unable to release that retainer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_FAILED<tab>Вам не удалось отпустить этого слугу.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FAILED<tab>Your application for a retainer was denied.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FAILED<tab>Ваша заявка на найм слуги была отклонена.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CALL_FAILED<tab>Your retainer could not be summoned.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CALL_FAILED<tab>Не удалось призвать вашего слугу.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_MARKET_FAILED<tab>The retainer was unable to make the trip.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_MARKET_FAILED<tab>The retainer was unable to make the trip.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_NAME_TOO_SHORT<tab>Nicknames must be between 3 and 20 characters.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_NAME_TOO_SHORT<tab>Псевдонимы должны быть от 3 до 20 символов.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CONTRACT_ENDED<tab>This retainer's contract has been suspended.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CONTRACT_ENDED<tab>Контракт с этим слугой был приостановлен.
